Mexican Cuisine and Cantina serves fresh Mexican & Tex-Mex food and Legendary Margaritas! Huge portions, indoor and patio seating, a diverse selection of cocktails and an unusually inviting atmosphere make us one of the hottest spots in town! For an authentic Mexican experience, come to Tijuana! Conveniently located in Davie, Coral Springs and Deerfield Beach. We are a family and friend locally owned and operated restaurant group in South Florida. We opened our first location in Davie in October 2004. Our passion for serving you allowed us to open our second and third locations in Coral Springs and Deerfield Beach. We love what we do and we sincerely hope that you do too!
